extendedInfo.description: Looking for that great comeback when your friends are talking trash? Look no further! Check out our collections of yo momma jokes, men and women jokes, and put downs that will be sure to get some laughs and put your friends in their place! View the jokes by category if you have a specific target, otherwise you can view all the jokes at once!Keywords: Trash Talk, Insults, Funny, Hilarious, Jokes, Yo Mama, Mamma, Male, Female,

reviews.comment: Fun quick little app. Gave me a chuckle.

reviews.title: Funny Insults
